{"article_id":"WiRHlY8Q9cC9JTVo","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In a series of tweets , Trump said","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"Esper fired Spencer ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"and he criticized Spencer both for his handling of the Gallagher case and for other aspects of his performance as Navy secretary .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"\" I was not pleased with the way","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that Navy Seal Eddie Gallagher ' s trial was handled by the Navy , \"","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Trump wrote on Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"\" He was treated very badly","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"but ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"despite this , was completely exonerated on all major charges .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"I then restored Eddie ' s rank .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Likewise , large cost overruns from past administration ' s contracting procedures were not addressed to my satisfaction .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Therefore , Secretary of the Navy Richard Spencer ' s services have been terminated by Secretary of Defense Mark Esper . \"","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Trump didn ' t specify","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"which contracting issues he meant ,","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"but he and Spencer have butted heads over the delivery schedule of the Navy ' s next aircraft carrier , the USS Gerald Ford .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"Delays have plagued the carrier ' s weapons elevators ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"and Spencer publicly bet Trump last January","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"if the problems weren ' t resolved by the next time","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"the warship put out to sea ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"the president could fire him","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"- only for the carrier to conduct sea trials last month","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"with only some of its elevators working .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Trump ' s relationship with his administration ' s top Pentagon leaders has been marked by increasing turmoil over the past year ,","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"starting with retired Gen. Jim Mattis ' resignation as Defense secretary in December after a presidential order ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"which was later partly reversed ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"to pull U.S. troops out of Syria .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Trump has since gone through three acting Defense secretaries","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"- including , briefly , Spencer -","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"before Esper was confirmed in July .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"On Esper ' s watch , Trump has again ordered a pullout from Syria ,","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"only to again partially reverse it under pressure from the Pentagon and Congress .","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"Sen. Jim Inhofe","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"( R-Okla. ) ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"chairman of the Armed Services Committee , said in a statement :","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"\" Both Secretary Esper and President Trump deserve to have a leadership team","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"who has their trust and confidence .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"It is no secret","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"that I had my own disagreements with Secretary Spencer over the management of specific Navy programs ,","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"and I look forward to receiving and considering a nomination for the next Secretary of the Navy as soon as possible . \"","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"Gallagher was acquitted over the summer of murdering a wounded prisoner in Iraq","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"but convicted of posing for a photo with the militant ' s body","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"and was demoted .","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"Days after Trump restored Gallagher ' s rank earlier this month ,","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"Navy officials said","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"the top admiral","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"responsible for the SEALs","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"was notifying Gallagher and three of his superior officers","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that boards were being convened","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"to consider expelling them from the commando unit .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"\" I hereby acknowledge my termination as United States Secretary of the Navy ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"to be effective immediately , \"","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Spencer wrote in a letter to Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"which was posted on Twitter by CNN .","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"Spencer did not refer in the letter to the communications with the White House","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"that the Pentagon cited in its announcement .","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"Outgoing Secretary of the Navy Spencer ' s acknowledgment-of-termination letter says","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"that he \" can not in good conscience \" obey an order","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"he believes","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"\" violates the sacred oath \"","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"he took","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"& that he and POTUS disagree on the \" key principle of good order and discipline \"","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"pic.twitter.com/EZ8YPM7M0L","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"- Jake Tapper","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"( @ jaketapper )","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"November 24 , 2019","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"\" Unfortunately it has become apparent that ... I no longer share the same understanding with the Commander in Chief","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"who appointed me ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"in regards to the key principle of good order and discipline .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"I can not in good conscience obey an order","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that I believe","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"violates the sacred oath","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"I took in the presence of my family , my flag and my faith","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"to support and defend the Constitution of the United States , \"","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"he wrote , in an apparent reference to Trump ' s direction","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"that the Navy not eject Gallagher from the SEALs .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"After Esper and Joint Chiefs Chairman Gen. Mark Milley spoke with Trump about Gallagher ' s case on Friday ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Hoffman said ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"\" Secretary Esper learned","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"that Secretary Spencer had previously and privately proposed to the White House","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"- contrary to Spencer ' s public position -","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"to restore Gallagher ' s rank","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"and allow him to retire with his Trident pin . \"","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"Despite asking for Spencer ' s resignation over the proposal , though ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Esper \" has directed","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"that Gallagher retain his Trident pin , \" the insignia","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"that marks him as a SEAL ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"Hoffman said .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"\" Eddie Gallagher ' s and his family ' s fervent hope is that this truly is the end of the road","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and he can go into retirement \" as a SEAL ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"said Timothy Parlatore , Gallagher ' s lawyer .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Whatever the apparent mismatch between the Pentagon statement and Spencer ' s letter , Trump ' s unusual intervention in the Gallagher case is at the root of the clash","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"that led to Spencer ' s departure ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"former Navy Secretary Ray Mabus said .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"\" This all started with the president .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"We wouldn ' t be here","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"if it wasn ' t for his actions ,","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"and I don ' t think","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"you can lose sight of that , \"","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"said Mabus ,","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"who held the top Navy post in the Obama administration .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"\" He undermined good order and discipline .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"He dishonored the SEALs","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"by saying","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"they couldn ' t hold a review board .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"So that ' s what got us into this mess .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"This is just one more example","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"showing","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"if you deal with this president ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"it ' s not going to end well . \"","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"\" It ' s typical Trump , \"","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"agreed a former senior Defense official","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"who spoke on condition of anonymity","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"to discuss a situation","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"in which the facts are unclear .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"\" This is the Trump circus .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Everything","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"he touches","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"turns into this convoluted process of politics","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that we ' re seeing today over at the Pentagon . \"","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Trump said","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"he will nominate Rear Adm. Kenneth Braithwaite , the ambassador to Norway ,","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"to replace Spencer as Navy secretary .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"And Esper will meet Monday morning","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"\" to discuss the way ahead \"","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"with Chief of Naval Operations Adm. Michael Gilday and the service ' s new acting secretary , Thomas Modly ,","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"said Hoffman .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":255,"left":159,"right":254,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":150,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":139,"right":149,"relation":"elaborati